' description: append_issue_context 4 道守门决策树 — not-found / source-bound / resolved / 软删 reject
' last_updated: 2026-05-31
@startuml issue-tracker-append-decision

title append_issue_context — 4 道守门决策树 (source-bound + resolved + 软删 reject)

' 守门顺序与 handler 实现一致; 详细 hint 文案 / REVIEW 见 INDEX 第 3 列

start
:append_issue_context(issueId, additionalContext, logsRef?);
note right
  deny external caller — 写 issues + issue_appendices
  + source-bound 校验需真实 in-process callerSessionId
end note

:issue = issueRepo.get(issueId);
if (issue 不存在?) then (是)
  :reject "issue not found";
  stop
else (否)
endif

if (issue.sourceSessionId != callerSessionId?) then (是)
  :reject — 跨 session / 跨 caller;
  note right
    §不变量 3 strict source-bound
    hint: 改用 report_issue 重新上报新 issue, UI 人工 merge
    (agent 重启 / hand_off 后丢 issueId 走这条)
  end note
  stop
else (否)
endif

if (issue.status == 'resolved'?) then (是)
  :reject — resolved 不接受 append;
  note right
    避免 resolved issue 被续命让 GC 时钟错位
    翻回重开: 源/解决会话经 update_issue_status({status:'in-progress'})
    或 UI 手工改回, 再 append (CHANGELOG_189)
  end note
  stop
else (否)
endif

if (issue.deletedAt != null?) then (是)
  :reject — 已软删 (UI 隐藏);
  note right
    与 resolved-reject 对称
    UI 恢复后再 append 或 report_issue 重报
  end note
  stop
else (否)
endif

:issueRepo.appendContext;
:INSERT issue_appendices (不动 issues.description §不变量 9);
:logsRef merge §D17 (date 覆盖 / tsRange min-max / scopes union / note 追加);
:emit issue-changed kind='appended' (含 appendices §D19);
:ok(IssueRecord + appendices);
stop

@enduml
